News.headline: Loan Announcement: Tyrique Hyde Joins Whitehawk FC
News.page_title: Loan Announcement: Tyrique Hyde Joins Whitehawk FC
News.URL_keywords: Loan Announcement: Tyrique Hyde Joins Whitehawk FC
News.short_description: Tyrique Hyde has joined Whitehawk FC on loan until the 13th March 2017
News.description:
The Daggers can announce that midfielder Tyrique Hyde has signed a one month loan with National League South club Whitehawk FC until Monday 13th March 2017.

The midfielder signed his first pro contract with the Daggers in August 2016 and has made nine appearances, scoring one goal for the club.

Follow us on our Social Media sites for updates on how Tyrique Hyde is doing on his loan spell at Whitehawk FC.
